America West Airlines.
YOU'RE FREE TO GO
JOIN FLIGHTFUND AND FLY FREE TO EUROPE, ASIA, HAWAII
AND OVER 45 U.S. DESTINATIONS
Leave at your leisure! America West's popular frequent
flyer program, FlightFund, is a quick, easy way to earn tickets
to see the world…free. When you fly on America West, you'll
earn valuable FlightFund miles. You'll also receive bonus
miles for flying First Class, Business Class or Full-Fare Coach,
plus additional miles for purchasing an America West
Vacations package or for using your FlightFund VISA® Card.
We'll even throw in mileage credit when you fly on our
partners, Aeromexico and Virgin Atlantic Airways.
And, you don't have to be a world traveler to get big
mileage credit. Even the shortest trip earns you a minimum
of 750 miles per flight. But flying isn't the only way to get
FlightFund mileage credit. You'll earn miles every time you
rent a Budget or Thrifty car or stay at a Doubletree Hotel,
Doubletree Club Hotel or Westin Hotel... in conjunction
with an America West flight.
Before you know it, you'll be free to go. After you earn
just 20,000 FlightFund miles, you'll automatically receive
mileage award certificates which can be redeemed at any
America West ticket counter, even for spur-of-the moment
travel. Better yet, you'll get a 2,500 mile enrollment bonus, so
join today. Pick up an application at any America West ticket
counter or call 800-247-5691.
flight Fund®
